        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. All tested patients must be Sobriety and coordination the examination.

          2. All tested patients with motor nerve fiber damaged must tally with the diagnosis
             standard which after the head CT, fMRI confirmation and obvious clinical symptoms.

          3. Patient's age and gender: 20—65years，the gender is not limit;

          4. All patient's must has one side neurological deficits.

          5. The patient must receive surgery and stem cell transplantation.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Progressive dysfunction;

          2. Other internal organs strict illness sickness, like serious heart disease, diabetes,
             liver, kidney vigorous sickness and so on;

          3. The patient with tumor in every system on there body;

          4. Having the primary or the sequential epilepsy medical history, within one year had the
